AWS CloudWatch (Monitoring Service)
Working with CloudWatch:
Describe CloudWatch alarms:
 
 
aws cloudwatch describe-alarms
Create a CloudWatch alarm:
 
 
aws cloudwatch put-metric-alarm --alarm-name my-alarm --comparison-operator GreaterThanThreshold --evaluation-periods 1 --metric-name my-metric --namespace my-namespace --period 300 --statistic Average --threshold 50 --actions-enabled --alarm-actions arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:123456789012:my-sns-topic
List CloudWatch metrics:
 
 
aws cloudwatch list-metrics
Get metric statistics:
 
 
aws cloudwatch get-metric-statistics --namespace my-namespace --metric-name my-metric --start-time 2024-05-01T00:00:00Z --end-time 2024-05-01T23:59:59Z --period 300 --statistics Average
Delete a CloudWatch alarm:
 
 
aws cloudwatch delete-alarms --alarm-name my-alarm
